  "markup": "Dr. Christopher Carraway of LTU interviews Ernesto Leal Junior, PhD, PT, Professor-Nove de Julho University, Sao Paulo, Brazil at the NAALT/WALT joint meeting in Washington, DC, September 2014.\u0026nbsp; Dr. Leal Junior gives his insights on skeletal muscle fatigue research being conducted with low level laser on Athletes, and his goals for education of clinicians in daily practice on this research, along with what is currently being investigated in his lab.\u0026nbsp; Dr. Leal Junior was a presenter in the pre-conference and general session."
}]]></Value>
